  "prompt": "What are the best places to stay in munnar?",
  "response": "Munnar, a picturesque hill station in Kerala, India, offers a variety of accommodation options to suit different preferences and budgets. Here are some of the best places to stay in Munnar:\n\n1. **Luxury Resorts:**\n   - **The Panoramic Getaway:** Known for its breathtaking views and luxurious amenities, including a heated pool and fine dining.\n   - **SpiceTree Munnar:** Offers a unique blend of luxury and nature, with private pool villas and spa services.\n   - **Fragrant Nature Munnar:** A luxury resort with beautiful views and premium facilities.\n\n2. **Mid-Range Hotels:**\n   - **The Munnar Queen:** Offers comfortable rooms with great views and modern amenities at reasonable prices.\n   - **Elysium Gardens Hill Resorts:** A charming place offering comfortable stays and good service.\n   - **Devonshire Greens:** A nice blend of comfort, fantastic views, and good service.\n\n3. **Budget Accommodations:**\n   - **Zina Cottage:** A quaint and affordable choice with cozy rooms.\n   - **Green View Inn:** Functional and budget-friendly with basic amenities.\n   - **Munnar Castle:** Affordable yet comfortable, with a good location.\n\n4. **Homestays:**\n   - **The Shade Homestay:** Offers personalized service and a cozy atmosphere with beautiful surroundings.\n   - **Rose Garden Homestay:** Known for its warm hospitality and charming garden.\n   - **Mistletoe Munnar:** A homestay with magnificent views and a homely feel, perfect for a relaxing stay.\n\n5. **Eco-Friendly Stays:**\n   - **Eco Tones Munnar:** Focuses on eco-tourism and offers unique experiences in harmony with nature.\n   - **Windermere Estate:** Combines rustic charm with modern conveniences in a beautiful natural setting.\n\nEach of these accommodations provides a unique experience, catering to different tastes and budgets. It's advisable to book in advance, especially during peak tourist seasons, and check recent reviews and ratings for the best current insight into services and amenities.",
